2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper focuses on relay channels, which are a fundamental concept in networking and internet architecture.
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses joint power allocation algorithms, which are relevant to systems and control.
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper does not explicitly deal with multimedia, but the concept of energy efficiency is relevant to multimedia applications.
5. cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) - The paper does not explicitly deal with computational engineering, finance, or science, but the algorithms and numerical results presented in the paper involve computational methods.
